    <div class="py-2">
      <text class="text-lg">
        Currently pursuing a B.S. in Biomedical Engineering, with a minor in Chemistry at Duke University. I am passionate about exploring the relationship of engineering, science, and medicine, and my coursework in Biomedical Engineering and Chemistry have provided me with a strong foundation for my future in the field. 
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a class="btn" href="mailto:nicholas.trigger@duke.edu" target="_blank"> Let's connect!</a>
